{
  "id": "69a64b33063d2df293c1374f",
  "title": "要件定義",
  "created": 1772505911,
  "updated": 1772505976,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69a64b33063d2df293c1374f",
      "text": "要件定義",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505911,
      "updated": 1772505911
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b3600000000004af8fb",
      "text": "[ふーことましろとひよりの会話]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505911,
      "updated": 1772505919
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b3800000000004af8fc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505913,
      "updated": 1772505913
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7600000000004af8fd",
      "text": "――放課後の図書室。ノートPCを広げた三人。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505975,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af8fe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af8ff",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]（進行係）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af900",
      "text": "はいはいみんな注目〜！今日のテーマは「要件定義」ね！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af901",
      "text": "ぶっちゃけさ、これミスるとプロジェクト即・南無三ってやつじゃん？草。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af902",
      "text": "ってことで、まずは「要件定義って何なん？」からいこ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af903",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af904",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]（やさしく）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af905",
      "text": "うん、いいね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af906",
      "text": "要件定義っていうのはね、「どんなものを作るのか」を最初にちゃんと決めること、かな。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af907",
      "text": "たとえば「便利なアプリを作りたい」だけじゃ足りなくて、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af908",
      "text": "「誰が」「何のために」「どんな場面で使うのか」を整理する作業なの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af909",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af90a",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]（淡々と）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af90b",
      "text": "補足すると、要件定義は“作る前の設計図の設計”だね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af90c",
      "text": "いきなり作り始めると、目的と手段がズレる確率が高い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af90d",
      "text": "統計的にも、システム開発の失敗原因の上位は「要件の不明確さ」とされている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af90e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af90f",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af910",
      "text": "出た、ひよりのデータ砲。つよい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af911",
      "text": "でもさ、現場って「とりあえず作ってみよ！」ってなりがちじゃん？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af912",
      "text": "文化祭の出し物レベルでもそうだよね？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af913",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af914",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af915",
      "text": "あるあるだね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af916",
      "text": "でもね、途中で「やっぱりこれも欲しい」「思ってたのと違う」ってなると、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af917",
      "text": "作り直しが大変になるの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af918",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af919",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af91a",
      "text": "コストが指数的に増える。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af91b",
      "text": "後からの変更は、早い段階の変更より数倍〜数十倍の手間がかかるという研究もある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af91c",
      "text": "だから最初に決める価値が高い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af91d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af91e",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af91f",
      "text": "つまりさ、「後から修正＝地獄」ってことね。了解。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af920",
      "text": "じゃあさ、要件定義って具体的に何決めんの？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af921",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af922",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af923",
      "text": "大きく分けて二つ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af924",
      "text": "一つは「何をできるようにするか」。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af925",
      "text": "もう一つは「どれくらいちゃんと動くべきか」。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af926",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af927",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af928",
      "text": "翻訳しまーす！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af929",
      "text": "前者は「機能」ね。ボタン押したら投稿できる、とか。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af92a",
      "text": "後者は「性能」ね。サクサク動くとか、落ちないとか。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af92b",
      "text": "合ってる？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af92c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af92d",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af92e",
      "text": "正確。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af92f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af930",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]（微笑む）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af931",
      "text": "ふーこ、わかりやすいね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af932",
      "text": "「何ができるか」と「どれくらい安心して使えるか」ってことだね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af933",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af934",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af935",
      "text": "でさ、ここで事故るのが「みんな思ってることが違う問題」なんよ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af936",
      "text": "先生は「簡単なサイト」って言うけど、生徒は「SNSみたいなやつ」想像してたり。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af937",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af938",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af939",
      "text": "認識のズレ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af93a",
      "text": "人は自分の前提を言語化しない傾向がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af93b",
      "text": "だから質問が重要になる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af93c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af93d",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af93e",
      "text": "うんうん。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af93f",
      "text": "「簡単って、どれくらい？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af940",
      "text": "「誰が使うの？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af941",
      "text": "って、優しく確認するのが大事だね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af942",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af943",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af944",
      "text": "要するに、空気読まずにガンガン聞けってことね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af945",
      "text": "「それって具体的には？」を連打。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af946",
      "text": "コミュ力ゲーじゃん…。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af947",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af948",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af949",
      "text": "コミュニケーションは技術。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af94a",
      "text": "感覚ではなく、構造で考えられる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af94b",
      "text": "目的→利用者→場面→必要な機能、の順に分解する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af94c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af94d",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af94e",
      "text": "ひよりの考え方、整理されていて好きだな。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af94f",
      "text": "上から順番に決めていくのね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af950",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af951",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af952",
      "text": "トップダウン思考ってやつね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af953",
      "text": "いきなり「ボタン何色？」とか言い出すのは事故、と。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af954",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af955",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af956",
      "text": "優先順位が逆転している。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af957",
      "text": "本質は「なぜ作るか」。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af958",
      "text": "そこが曖昧だと、全部ブレる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af959",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af95a",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]（共感気味に）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af95b",
      "text": "でも、最初にそこまで考えるのって、ちょっと怖くない？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af95c",
      "text": "間違ってたらどうしよう、って。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af95d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af95e",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af95f",
      "text": "だから仮説として定義する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af960",
      "text": "絶対ではない。更新可能な前提。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af961",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af962",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af963",
      "text": "あー、それいいね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af964",
      "text": "「いったんこれでいこ！」って決めるけど、あとで見直せる前提。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af965",
      "text": "固定じゃなくて、暫定。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af966",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af967",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af968",
      "text": "完璧じゃなくていい、ってことだね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af969",
      "text": "ちゃんと話し合って決めた、という状態が大事なんだね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af96a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af96b",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]（まとめに入る）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af96c",
      "text": "じゃあ今日の結論いくよ〜！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af96d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af96e",
      "text": " 要件定義＝「何作るか」をちゃんと決めるターン",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af96f",
      "text": " 機能（何できる？）と性能（どれくらいちゃんと？）を分ける",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af970",
      "text": " ズレは起こる前提。質問しまくれ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af971",
      "text": " 目的から順に決める。いきなり細部はNG",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af972",
      "text": " 完璧じゃなくていいけど、合意は必要",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af973",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af974",
      "text": "こんな感じ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af975",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af976",
      "text": "[[ひより.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af977",
      "text": "妥当。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af978",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af979",
      "text": "[[ましろ.icon]]（やわらかく笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af97a",
      "text": "うん、とてもいいまとめだと思うよ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af97b",
      "text": "最初に丁寧に決めることが、あとでみんなを助けるんだね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af97c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af97d",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af97e",
      "text": "よし、これで文化祭アプリも爆死回避！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af97f",
      "text": "要件定義、ナメたらあかんやつでした〜！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af980",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    },
    {
      "id": "69a64b7700000000004af981",
      "text": "三人、ノートを見つめながら次の議題へ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1772505976,
      "updated": 1772505976
    }
  ]
}